quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  33,41,oh inu anthu okhulupirira! Kumbukirani Mulungu ndipo muzimukumbukira pafupipafupi
  33,42,Ndipo muyamikeni m’mawa ndi madzulo aliwonse
  33,43,Ndiye amene amapereka madalitso ake pa inu ndipo angelo ake amachita chimodzimodzi kuti Iye akhoza kukuchotsani inu ku mdima kupita kowala. Ndipo Iye ndi wachifundo kwa okhulupirira
  33,44,"Kulonjerana kwawo pa tsiku limene adzakumana naye kudzakhala adzati,“Mtendere”. Ndipo Iye wawakonzera mphotho yolemekezeka"
  33,45,Oh iwe Mtumwi! Ndithudi takutumiza iwe ngati mboni ndi wobweretsa nkhani yabwino ndi wochenjeza
  33,46,Ngati munthu woitana anthu kuti adze kwa Mulungu ndi chilolezo chake ndiponso ngati Muuni
  33,47,Kotero auze nkhani yabwino anthu okhulupirira kuti adzalandira mphatso yaikulu kuchokera kwa Mulungu
  33,48,Ndipo usamvere zilakolako za anthu osakhulupirira ndi za anthu a chinyengo. Usalabadire zonena zawo koma ika chikhulupiriro chako mwa Mulungu. Mulungu ndi wokwana kukhala Mtetezi
  33,49,"Oh inu anthu okhulupirira! Pamene mukwatira akazi okhulupirira ndipo muwasudzula musanalowane nawo, palibe nthawi yoyembekezera pakhomo panu. Kotero asanachoke apatseni mphatso yawo ndipo alekeni kuti achoke mwaubwino"
  33,50,"Oh iwe Mtumwi! Takulola kukhala ndi akazi onse amene iwe wapereka chiongo chawo ndi iwo amene ndi akapolo ako kuchokera kugulu limene lidagwidwa pankhondo ndipo Mulungu wakupatsa iwe; ana a akazi a atsibweni ndi azakhali ako, a kuchimuna kapena kuchikazi amene adachoka pamodzi ndi iwe. Ndiponso mkazi wina aliyense wokhulupirira amene adzipereka yekha kwa Mtumwi ngati Mtumwi afuna kumukwatira iye. Chilolezo ichi ndi cha iwe wekha osati cha anthu onse okhulupirira. Ife tikudziwa chimene tawasankhira iwo zokhudza akazi awo ndi akapolo amene iwo amasunga, ndi cholinga chakuti pasadzakhale vuto kwa iwe. Ndipo Mulungu amakhululukira nthawi zonse ndipo ndiye Mwini chisoni chosatha"
  33,51,Iwe ukhoza kumusiya aliyense wa iwo amene wafuna ndipo ukhoza kutenga aliyense wa iwo amene wafuna ndi aliyense wa iwo amene udawasiya pa kanthawi kochepa. Palibe cholakwa kwa iwe pochita izi kuti maso awo azizire ndiponso onse asadandaule ndi zimene uwapatsa. Ndipo Mulungu amadziwa zinthu zonse zomwe zili m’mitima mwanu. Mulungu amadziwa zonse ndiponso ndi wopirira
  33,52,Iwe siuloledwa kukwatiranso akazi ena pambuyo pa awa kapena kuwasintha kuti upeze akazi ena ngakhale kuti kukongola kwawo kuli kukusangalatsa kupatula akapolo amene uli nawo. Ndipo Mulungu amayang’anitsitsa pa zinthu zonse